\c 8
\s Abantwana bakoIsrayeli bafuna inkosi
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi uSamuweli esemdala wabeka\x + Dute. 16.18.\x* amadodana akhe ukuze abe ngabahluleli koIsrayeli\x + Hlu. 10.4. 12.14. Hlu. 5.10.\x*.
\v 2 Lebizo lendodana yakhe elizibulo lalinguJoweli, lebizo leyesibili linguAbhiya; ayengabahluleli eBherishebha\x + Josh. 15.28.\x*.
\v 3 Kodwa amadodana akhe ayengahambi ngendlela zakhe, kodwa aphambukela enzuzweni embi\x + Eks. 18.21.\x*, emukela isivalamlomo, aphambula isahlulelo\x + Eks. 23.8. Hlab. 15.5.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Kwasekubuthana abadala bonke bakoIsrayeli, beza kuSamuweli eRama\x + 1.19.\x*,
\v 5 bathi kuye: Khangela, wena usumdala, lamadodana akho kawahambi ngendlela zakho; ngakho sibekele inkosi ukuze isahlulele njengazo zonke izizwe\x + 8.19,20. Dute. 17.14. Hos. 13.10. Seb. 13.21.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Kodwa leyonto yayimbi emehlweni kaSamuweli lapho besithi: Sinike inkosi ukusahlulela. USamuweli wasekhuleka eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 7 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuSamuweli: Lalela ilizwi labantu kukho konke abakutshoyo kuwe, ngoba kakusuwe abakwalayo\x + Eks. 16.8.\x*, kodwa bala mina ukuze ngingabusi phezu kwabo\x + Hlu. 8.23.\x*.
\v 8 Ngokwezenzo zonke abazenzileyo kusukela ngosuku engabenyusa ngalo eGibhithe kuze kube lamuhla, bangitshiyile bakhonza abanye onkulunkulu; benza njalo lakuwe.
\v 9 Ngakho khathesi, lalela ilizwi labo; kodwa nxa ubafakazele kakhulu, ubazise indlela yenkosi ezabusa phezu kwabo\x + 8.11-18.\x*.
\p
\v 10 USamuweli wasetshela abantu abacela kuye inkosi wonke amazwi eN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 11 Wasesithi: Le izakuba yindlela yenkosi ezabusa phezu kwenu\x + 10.25. Dute. 17.16.\x*; izathatha amadodana enu izibekele wona enqoleni zayo lakubagadi bamabhiza ayo, agijime phambi kwezinqola zayo\x + 14.52.\x*.
\v 12 Izazibekela wona abe yizinduna zezinkulungwane lezinduna zamatshumi amahlanu, lokulima amasimu ayo, lokuvuna isivuno sayo, lokwenza izikhali zayo zempi, lezikhali zezinqola zayo\x + Gen. 45.6.\x*.
\v 13 Izathatha amadodakazi enu iwenze abe ngabenzi bamakha, labapheki, labaphekizinkwa\x + Eks. 30.25.\x*.
\v 14 Izathatha amasimu enu, lezivini zenu lezivande zenu zemihlwathi, ezinhle, ikunike inceku zayo.
\v 15 Izathatha okwetshumi yenhlanyelo yenu leyezivini zenu, iyinike induna zayo lenceku zayo\x + 1 Kho. 21.7. Hez. 46.18.\x*.
\v 16 Izathatha inceku zenu lencekukazi zenu lamajaha enu angcono labobabhemi benu, ikusebenzise emsebenzini wayo.
\v 17 Izathatha okwetshumi kwemihlambi yenu; lina-ke libe yizinceku zayo.
\v 18 Njalo lizakhala ngalolosuku ngenxa yenkosi yenu elizikhethele yona; kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* kayiyikuliphendula mhlalokho\x + Mika 3.4. Zaga 1.28.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Kodwa abantu bala ukulilalela ilizwi likaSamuweli, bathi: Hatshi, kodwa kuzakuba lenkosi phezu kwethu,
\v 20 ukuze lathi sibe njengezizwe zonke\x + 8.5.\x*, lenkosi yethu isahlulele, iphume phambi kwethu, ilwe izimpi zethu.
\v 21 USamuweli esewazwile wonke amazwi abantu, wawalandisa endlebeni zeN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 22 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuSamuweli: Lalela ilizwi labo, ubabekele inkosi\x + 8.7. Hos. 13.11.\x*. USamuweli wasesithi emadodeni akoIsrayeli: Hambani liye ngulowo lalowo emzini wakhe.
